data.description: Easy, main-level living in the sought-after Fairmont on the Park community, nestled in the highly desirable Dacula school district. The property boasts a generous .24-acre lot providing ample space for outdoor activities, gardening and play in the fenced backyard. Upon arrival, you'll appreciate the level driveway parking, offering convenience and curb appeal. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed, open, ranch-style home on a full basement just perfect for an expanding family. The heart of this home lies in its inviting common rooms for entertaining and creating cherished memories. The vaulted living room features a cozy fireplace and built in bookshelves. Large windows flood the room with natural light, showcasing the beauty of the surrounding outdoors. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space and an abundance of cabinets for all your storage needs. Whether you're hosting a family gathering or a dinner party, the adjoining dining area offers an extended space to savor delectable meals and engaging conversations or an easy conversion to a main level office. Escape to your private retreat in the master suite, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom that includes a soaking tub, separate shower and dual vanities. Two additional main level bedrooms provide ample space for family or guests serviced by a hall bathroom.  But that's not all - head downstairs to discover the full basement to create your dream entertainment space, a home gym, or an inspiring home office - the possibilities are endless. Two private bedrooms and a full bath on this level allows for maximum flexibility. Living in the Fairmont on the Park community grants you access to a host of amenities including swimming pool, tennis courts, playground, clubhouse, nearby parks, walking trails and a friendly neighborhood atmosphere. And with the top-rated schools of Dacula just moments away, you can be assured of a quality education for your family. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a home that perfectly blends comfort, charm, and functionality. Schedule your showing today and embrace the lifestyle that awaits you in this fantastic property. Welcome home!
